{
  "stem": "19807.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 299.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's just-- --when we were told that our lives were spared, every-- we-- we broke off-- we-- we were crying, we were-- we were-- [SIGHS] --singing 'God Bless the King' and-- and we were singing the national anthem and we were kissing each other and-- and-- and hugging each other.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- we just couldn't believe we got home and-- and our lives had been spared, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] --and sad thing was that shortly after that I remember the-- the change of government and I remember all these things are beginning to happen.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one night, I remember in the middle of the night, the bells began to ring all over the city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I can feel the anxiety in my mother and father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- was it was an announcement that you could hear through the sound of the bells.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It had to be for something really big to happen for them to be ringing all over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all we said in the world was all-- all over town, the king is dead.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] --there had been allegations that the king was poisoned by the Germans for two reasons.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One of them is the reluctance to turn the Jews of Bulgaria to the Nazis, to turn them in and to send him to the camps.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the other was his flat refusal to the Germans to have the Bulgarian Army fight on the Eastern Front against Russia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, you have to understand something very quickly about the Bulgarian people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If they have a monkey running Russia, they would be loyal to Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
